snippet.title: Stock Market Tycoon: Challenge! Available on Steam and mobile.
snippet.description:
A detailed multiplayer stock market investment game. Stock Market Tycoon: Challenge! - Released on App Store and Google Play store. #stockmarketgame #stockmarkettycoon

Released to PC December 6.
Play on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3296800?utm_source=yt&utm_campaign=vidpromo
Get it on the App Store:
https://apps.apple.com/au/app/stock-market-tycoon-challenge/id6680189788
Get it on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.AethernaGames.StockMarketTycoon

Music from #Uppbeat (free for Creators!):
https://uppbeat.io/t/tatami/journey
